messages.message: I'm trying to access audit-logs on my crafting sandbox. I logged in to my crafting sandbox using the admin credentials documented here (https://instabase.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/ENG/pages/2881486881/Setting+up+your+Dev+Environment#Log-in-as-an-admin-(IB-Classic-Apps)) (i.e. `<mailto:noreply+admin@instabase.com|noreply+admin@instabase.com>`). When I do that, I can access the audit-log page (https://https--neerad-instabase.instabase.site.sandboxes.run/apps/audit-logs/), but the audit-logs are empty (I've done some operations using my regular non-admin user, so I expect non-empty audit-logs). Am I doing something wrong?

Hey! Could you try following this thread and see if it works for you?
